    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >末世旅人是一款开放世界的精美像素后末日生存RPG游戏。玩家将扮演猎人组织的骨干“马特”，前往末日来临时崩溃的重要关口--马里恩哨卡，在完成派系给予的任务的同时探索这个废弃要塞的秘密。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/5fabb8492d16fd73d0860ebe884d4196.poster.avif?t=1747144257\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/5fabb8492d16fd73d0860ebe884d4196.webm?t=1747144257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/5fabb8492d16fd73d0860ebe884d4196.mp4?t=1747144257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在2035年的夏天，丧尸病毒爆发、全球城市陷落：表面稳定且繁荣的五大巨企联合统治下的人类文明社会已彻底覆灭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在以生存为主题的后末日世界里，仅仅只是活着就已如履薄冰。你必须准备好面对许多棘手问题，包括补给的日益减少，恶劣天气，病毒辐射等，更要竭尽所能地避开疯狂的丧尸，虎视眈眈的智械，变异生物的攻击与茫茫废土中“豺狼”们的掠夺。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/ec74d171c6dd0c69246f78139fd21861.poster.avif?t=1747144257\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/ec74d171c6dd0c69246f78139fd21861.webm?t=1747144257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/ec74d171c6dd0c69246f78139fd21861.mp4?t=1747144257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >相较于其他末日生存游戏，末世旅人的正式版中有着更多需要你关心的任务，派系与NPC。设定在近未来的游戏背景提供了更多解决这些问题的手段。各种巨企生产的武器、药物、载具和现代工具，丰富精美的改枪系统，以上这些都能够帮助你活得更久、达成更多目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/e7ed572692f31bbfb5c968344195e58d.poster.avif?t=1747144257\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/e7ed572692f31bbfb5c968344195e58d.webm?t=1747144257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/e7ed572692f31bbfb5c968344195e58d.mp4?t=1747144257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      在末日后的世界，有四条规则需要特别强调。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      第一，放慢脚步，持续警戒。探索满目疮痍世界的同时也请小心在阴影里的丧尸和掠夺者们；注意可疑的各类巨企建筑。当然，风险也伴随着天大的收获和机遇。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/4e9e57aeeb8f169d222bb8e134cd7c8d.poster.avif?t=1747144257\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/4e9e57aeeb8f169d222bb8e134cd7c8d.webm?t=1747144257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/4e9e57aeeb8f169d222bb8e134cd7c8d.mp4?t=1747144257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第二，值得信任的人是维系生存的锚点。并非所有样貌可畏之人都是你的敌人，保持猜疑和戒备是幸存者的良好美德。尽量避免和不明势力的接触，随时注意检查自己营地周遭的情况；排查“豺狼”们隐设的陷阱以保卫自己的安全。但你依然可以找到合适的伙伴，同他们并肩战斗、共同生存，逐渐重建文明、恢复社会秩序；当然，伙伴也并不局限于人类… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     第三，请保持对未知的敬畏。即使在末世之中也依然无奇不有，派系之间的互相摩擦，以及末日前五大巨企不可思议的科技和掌控世界的密谋，越是接近北方的事变中心，解开真相的距离就越近。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第四，请务必按时服用PAX片剂！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/0cd0739ee56ea4aae7939aab81deed54.poster.avif?t=1747144257\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/0cd0739ee56ea4aae7939aab81deed54.webm?t=1747144257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275120/extras/0cd0739ee56ea4aae7939aab81deed54.mp4?t=1747144257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >废土欢迎您，幸存者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入我们的QQ粉丝群！9群：</strong>740132167</p>",
